Inbox ~/mail/mxtimmyd/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore mxtimmyd-remote
Host mx.timmyd.info
User timmy
PassCmd "gpg -dq ~/.password-store/timmydinfoimap.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

Channel mxtimmyd-channel
Far :mxtimmyd-remote:
Near :mxtimmyd-local:
Patterns INBOX * !Sync*
